{:event/actor "seb" :event/at #inst "2026-07-10T21:19:33.505Z" :event/body {:fact/path [:description] :fact/value "The store can live in a .tik directory and every command discovers its root git-style: TIK_ROOT, else the nearest ancestor with .tik, else the nearest ancestor with tickets/, else the cwd. tik init [--hidden] creates the skeleton and says so. A portfolio store above many repos becomes one dot-entry, reachable from anywhere beneath it."} :event/parents #{"sha256-6a7c37be327341ad926e5fd899b44db39a2fab48a17f66674b469e721518a08e"} :event/ticket #uuid "528795d9-37a5-4277-9403-35d7d6e1cba3" :event/type :fact/assert}